<HEADLINE> Denilson May Start in World Cup Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
PARIS, July 10 (Xinhua) -- Brazil super-bench Denilson may start
the final after he made an impact on the left with his speed and
ball skills in the semi-final against the Netherlands.
</P>
