points achieved amidst relatively high investment activity for the
period.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was contained to lower levels this week and was
3.7 million Cyprus pounds (about 7.4 million U.S. dollars) from
4.3 million pounds (about 8.6 million dollars) the previous week.
