Chinese Hall at the annual Malta International Exposition, which
is being attended by exhibitors from China, France, Germany,
Britain, the United States, Italy, Libya, Pakistan and Malta.
</P>
<P>
China-made light industry products, electronic home appliances,
and other commodities should be selling well here because the
Maltese people had enjoyed the good quality of Chinese goods over
a long time, President Bonnici told Chinese exhibitors.
</P>
