they like them, he added.
</P>
<P>
So Chinese commodities should have their market in Malta and
will enjoy a considerable slice of the market share, because they
are competitive in many aspects.
</P>
<P>
The most welcomed Chinese products at the exposition, the 41st
of its kind, included car television sets, which are made in
China's southern Fujian Province, fishing rods from Guangdong
Province, and cosmetics made in Beijing, an official of the
Chinese delegation said. 
