abandon nuclear option, which conforms to international trends.
</P>
<P>
A joint communique issued at the end of the meeting said the
Central Asian states have made progress in drafting legal
documents on the nuclear-free zone.
</P>
<P>
The participation of nuclear states in the consultation for the
establishment of the nuclear-free zone is helpful, the communique
said.
